rs at nationsbank in various leadership positions in retail finance and leasing charlie holds a bachelor’s degree in international economics and finance from georgetown university     who we are services leadership raymond j quinlan laurent c lutz steven j mcgarry charles p rocha jeffrey f dale history philanthropy contact sallie mae senior management we’re listening the office of the customer advocate reviews and responds to all customer inquiries addressed to the executive management staff of sallie mae working closely with teams within the company our customer advocates are dedicated to ensuring that your feedback is heard contact us      sallie mae bank all rights reserved sallie mae and the sallie mae logo are service marks or registered service marks of sallie mae bank or its subsidiaries all other names and logos used are the trademarks or service marks of their respective owners terms of use    protecting your privacy    avoid online fraud    beware of debt relief offers slm corporation and its subsidiaries including sallie mae bank and upromise inc are not sponsored by or agencies of the united states of america var csacctid  444 sallie mae promotes charles p rocha to executive vice president  sallie mae online newsroom login about who we are newsroom customer insights investors careers sallie mae promotes charles p rocha to executive vice president category corporate and financial friday july    am edt dateline newark del emailpdfprintrss public company information nasdaqslm as a parent of four daughters charlie understands what families go through to save plan and pay for college newark delbusiness wiresallie mae the nation’s saving planning and paying for college company today announced that charles p rocha has been named executive vice president mr rocha continues as the company’s chief marketing officer a position he has held since  overseeing product development sales marketing and communications for sallie mae’s consumer businesses including private 